name: Bibi
description: Bibi is the official mascot of Binance and the Binance ecosystem. It is a cute, yellow, cube-shaped character with a distinctive appearance that makes it easily recognizable. Bibi is often depicted in a playful and approachable manner, such as sitting at a desk with a laptop, symbolizing Binance's focus on technology and innovation. As the friendly face of Binance, Bibi helps to engage users and make the world of cryptocurrency more accessible and enjoyable.
